Rangers Football Club Says Its First-Half Profit Falls on Lower Revenue

-- B y   P e t e r   W o o d i f i e l d
-- 
2011-04-01T06:09:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-01/rangers-football-club-says-its-first-half-profit-falls-on-lower-revenue.html
Rangers Football Club Plc (RFC)  said
profit in the six months ended Dec. 31 fell to 9 million pounds
from 13.1 million pounds a year earlier as revenue declined to
33.7 million pounds from 37.8 million pounds a year earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter Woodifield at 
 pwoodifield@bloomberg.net  